OL,3,CCould the debate over this senior
OL,4,Cpolitician's role hurt a fair trial?
OL,6,FWritten by ITV News reporter Matthew
OL,7,FLeach
OL,9,FGuernsey's Policy and Resources
OL,10,FCommittee (P&R) has submitted a policy
OL,11,Fletter asking the island's politicians
OL,12,Fto approve the removal of Deputy
OL,13,FJonathan Le Tocq from the senior group.
OL,15,FIt's a mechanism that's rarely used,
OL,16,Fbut gives any committee the ability to
OL,17,Fremove a deputy if the majority of its
OL,18,Fmembers believe that the person's
OL,19,Fmembership "is unreasonably hindering
OL,20,Fthe ability of the Committee to fulfil
OL,21,Fits mandate".
