OL,3,CCould the debate over this senior
OL,4,Cpolitician's role hurt a fair trial?
OL,6,FThe motion must be voted through by
OL,7,Fthe Chamber and this requires debate.
OL,9,FDeputy Le Tocq has been charged with
OL,10,Fmultiple criminal offences, including
OL,11,Fpossessing thousands of indecent
OL,12,Fimages of children.
OL,14,FThe 61-year-old has also been charged
OL,15,Fwith possessing extreme pornography
OL,16,Fand offences relating to the misuse of
OL,17,Ftelecommunications.
