OL,3,CCould the debate over this senior
OL,4,Cpolitician's role hurt a fair trial?
OL,6,FHe is currently remanded in custody,
OL,7,Fhas not entered a plea and won't have
OL,8,Fdone so by the time this debate
OL,9,Fhappens on Wednesday 3 September.
OL,11,FThis is where Guernsey's politicians
OL,12,Fcould be facing a real test.
OL,14,FIf someone could theoretically be
OL,15,Fheading to trial, the law guides what
OL,16,Fpeople can publish or say to avoid
OL,17,Fimpeding the legal process.
