OL,3,CCould the debate over this senior
OL,4,Cpolitician's role hurt a fair trial?
OL,6,FGuernsey does not have a Contempt of
OL,7,FCourt Act like the UK, instead these
OL,8,Frestrictions are covered by a series
OL,9,Fof different parts of legislation.
OL,11,FMainly, it means stripping most of the
OL,12,Fdetail of a case out of the public
OL,13,Fconversation to avoid juries - or in
OL,14,Fthis case jurats - being swayed on a
OL,15,Fdecision before sitting through a
OL,16,Ftrial.
OL,18,FBut deputies are now heading for a
OL,19,Fdebate on whether or not Deputy Le
OL,20,FTocq should or shouldn't sit on Policy
OL,21,Fand Resources.
