OL,3,CCould the debate over this senior
OL,4,Cpolitician's role hurt a fair trial?
OL,6,FBut P&R don't have any other way of
OL,7,Freplacing one deputy with another on a
OL,8,Fcommittee, and they need a full
OL,9,Fcomplement as soon as possible to
OL,10,Ftackle the very real issues facing the
OL,11,Fisland.
OL,13,FDeputy Le Tocq was the island's
OL,14,FExternal Relations Lead - a role that
OL,15,Fis now being covered by Deputy Steve
OL,16,FFalla on an interim basis.
OL,18,FSo what protections are in place to
OL,19,Fmake sure the trial can go ahead
OL,20,Fwithout being prejudiced?
