OL,3,CCould the debate over this senior
OL,4,Cpolitician's role hurt a fair trial?
OL,6,FWell, the debate could be guillotined
OL,7,Fimmediately, forcing it straight to a
OL,8,Fvote, and I expect this is what will
OL,9,Fhappen. But once again, a guillotine
OL,10,Fmotion requires all members to agree
OL,11,Fvia a vote, and so might not be
OL,12,Fsuccessful.
OL,14,FHis Majesty's Procureur will also be
OL,15,Fon hand offering legal advice
OL,16,Fthroughout.
